      <title>Oracle、Google 资深人士加入 Nvidia 支持的 CoreWeave 领导 AI</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/oracle-google-veterans-join-nvidia-backed-coreweave-to-lead-ai</link>
